        <mxCell id="gtWbP-H09-lzMpGvogwt-26" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;More Info&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Here BasePizza and ToppingDecorator both are abstract classes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Here we have BasePizza as a &lt;b&gt;base object&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;and to which we are deocrating with another object (another object using which we are deocrating base object it &lt;b&gt;has-a&lt;/b&gt; base object). also another object is BasePizza only so&lt;b&gt; IS-A&lt;/b&gt; relation is used . To this another object if we want we can deocroate further&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1">
